1st leg. Casa Blanca, Quito, 25-11-2009
 
Liga de Quito: Alexander Domínguez; Carlos Espínola, Norberto Araujo,
  Diego Calderón; Néicer Reasco, Ulises De la Cruz, William Araujo,
  Miller Bolaños (68 Franklin Salas), Edison Méndez (84 Gonzalo Chila);
  Walter Calderón (68 Claudio Graf), Claudio Bieler; coach: Jorge Fossati;
